          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>A <fr:link href="hmlg-0008.xml" title="Chain map" addr="hmlg-0008" type="local">chain map</fr:link> is a <fr:strong>quasi-isomorphism</fr:strong> if it induces isomorphisms on the <fr:link href="hmlg-0007.xml" title="Components of a chain complex" addr="hmlg-0007" type="local">homology groups</fr:link>.</fr:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
